    "title": "Baasida.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Baasida has an emaciated light red body and a face from nightmares. Tiny orange flames dance around it.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 199     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++++ +   </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++++     </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: +         </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: ∞       </lightgrey><darkgrey>   rC: ...      </darkgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 140% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 81% to hit with the fire staff of Defence by Offence and 81% to hit with your bite and pseudopods.\nIt has about 74% to hit you.\n\nAttack                 Max Damage      \nTouch: electric touch  49 + 20 (elec)  \n\nIt has a 35% chance to notice you each turn.\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.",
